the grave of that dead, each angel carrying a saucer and saying to the dead, “Peace be upon you, O Allah’s intimate servant. This is the gift of so and so, the faithful, to you.” The grave of that dead will then glitter. Moreover, Almighty Allah will give him 1000 cities in Paradise, 1000 Paradisiacal women in marriage, 1000 garments to dress, and will grant him 1000 of his requests.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ek aur riwaayat mein hai keh jab koi shakhs kisi marne waale ko sawaab pohoncha ne ke liye sadqa karta hai to Allah (swt) Hazrat Jibraeel (a) ko hukm deta hai to woh 70000 farishto’n ke saath uski qabr par jaate hai jin mein se har ek haath mein neymate ilaahi ka tabqa hota hai, har farishte usko “Assalaamo alaika ya Wali Allah” kehta hai aur baata hai keh ay Khuda ke bande tumhaare liye yeh hadiya fula’n momin ne bheja hai. Uski qabr munawwar ho jaati hai aur Allah (swt) behisht (Jannat) mein uske 1000 shaher ataa farmaayega, 1000 hooro’n se uska aqd (nikah) karaayega, usey 1000 poshaaki (garments) pehnaayega aur uski 1000 haajaat puri farmaayega.", "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicTe